{"tid":1559944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近日藍絲捉跳閘愈黎愈癲，有以下建議","createTime":"2019-09-11T04:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T17:23:35.000Z","uid":16528,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2c6c595f6145a06aaf96cf602c62c1358878cc","tid":1559944,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不要對罵</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跳完就行，大聲講句關佢撚事就走。<br />\n嘈太耐比人拍片好撚麻煩<br />\n想郁手都留返係前線，<br />\n地鐵咁多人咁多cam好易比人周到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大叫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人捉住個陣麻煩大叫。<br />\n有時唔係唔想幫手，但一個站六七個位出閘，<br />\n有時真係無同路人都唔出奇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同路人一定要幫手</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲愈黎愈癲，仲要開始郁手，<br />\n同路人見到手足比人恰麻煩幫拖。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">買定張單程飛</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次入閘都扮嘟一野後先跳閘/爆閘，<br />\n比藍屍捉都即刻拎出黎話買咗飛。<br />\n出閘就直接跳，最撚驚都係入閘等車姐。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量唔好跳閘</span><br />\n舊既三腳閘（較長身個隻）可以直接大力爆開。<br />\n女仔都夠力，無人個陣試幾次先，試熟咗先落場。<br />\n港島就大部分都係新三腳機，幾大力都推唔開咖啦。<br />\n唔敢跳就可以去紅色閘門機用腳頂開or做跟尾狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申返先 825開始後日日坐狗鐵日日跳<br />\n主力跳欄跳閘同爆閘<br />\n比藍絲追屌過4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到還補充"},{"pid":"1fedf9eb5ca05f71f9ba0734ff59537d8f2df119","tid":1559944,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e21da05ac4f563d0825f49f25637b52554898a6","tid":1559944,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"9d64f159bedf35e1cfd35122bfd9c26f25cca696","tid":1559944,"uid":78957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"94574a0e2749af8cf1b032823766630f9a8d7aba","tid":1559944,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdcf740fee0475c14ec690a0018edc0fd3652cd","tid":1559944,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"其實啪咗卡可唔可以跳閘??"},{"pid":"1d13ad756e77484787c8b30efe01c0c9b7d63e9b","tid":1559944,"uid":198223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"有無想過, 點解最近藍絲咁團結, 又捉到跳閘.<br />\n我有工友 消息話$100一個鐘, 6人一組, 分兩間制, 係地鐵不同站, (周圍行)  見到人跳閘就折停佢地.<br />\n但工友不願比資料我, 近這幾天開始請人."},{"pid":"2023ef07bcb2278d7f563159ca632a0976e522a5","tid":1559944,"uid":163801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d13ad756e77484787c8b30efe01c0c9b7d63e9b","tid":1559944,"uid":198223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"有無想過, 點解最近藍絲咁團結, 又捉到跳閘.<br />\n我有工友 消息話$100一個鐘, 6人一組, 分兩間制, 係地鐵不同站, (周圍行)  見到人跳閘就折停佢地.<br />\n但工友不願比資料我, 近這幾天開始請人."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"我係跳閘咁又點?? 佢邊位可以截住人?? 你咪叫個職員過嚟囉~~<br />\n到有職員過嚟, 喂我啪晒卡有條粉人話我冇喎, 佢係咪職員我要投訴!! 唔係就可以亂咁捉人??"},{"pid":"3183494763091163fc1bc8c94b91be59eff4b507","tid":1559944,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cdcf740fee0475c14ec690a0018edc0fd3652cd","tid":1559944,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"其實啪咗卡可唔可以跳閘??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"可以，跳咗先算啦屌"},{"pid":"d511844d7bd8a87c97a07abcd820f90550491803","tid":1559944,"uid":16528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid"